data.description:
Experience Colorado Mountain living at its best with this exquisite single-family residence nestled in the coveted Cotton Ranch community. Embrace a lifestyle of leisure and out doors with access to an array of amenities including a pristine golf course, vibrant tennis and pickle ball courts, a charming restaurant, trails and a refreshing pool. Also minutes away from dirt bike and four-wheeler trails.
Short distance from Eagle Airport, and conveniently positioned within a 30-minute drive from the renowned Beaver Creek Ski Resort and a 45 minutes from the world-famous Vail Ski Resort, this home offers both convenience and affordability.
Step inside to discover a captivating living space adorned with soaring 2-story ceilings and a cozy gas fireplace that invites relaxation. Indulge your culinary passions in the fully upgraded, state-of-the-art kitchen complete with a convenient walk-in pantry. The main floor showcases a versatile dining room or den area, a bedroom or office, and a patio kitchen that beckons outdoor entertaining with Jacuzzi tub.
Ascend to the second floor to experience the master suite boasting spacious walk-in closet and ana 5-piece bathroom, setting the stage for pampered comfort.
The lower level is a haven of entertainment and comfort, featuring a well-appointed wet bar, guest room space, a media area, and room for recreational activities such as a pool table or ping pong. An additional unfinished area presents endless possibilities for hobbies or storage needs.
Parking is effortless with a 3-car garage offering ample space for all your outdoor gear and toys.
